name: About Me
bio: I'm a Sydney-based Programmer who recently made a big leap, dedicating the last ~6 months gaining experience in Xamarin.Forms, HTML/JS/CSS, React, ViteJS, Sass, Python, C# and more, learning new technologies excite me and finding solutions to problems is exhilarating, I am looking to take my development skills to the next level by finding a role where I can contribute as well as having some light guidance from an experienced mentor and team.
